@startuml traffic-flow-steady-state
!include ../../datum-theme-sequence.puml

participant "Client" as client <<Person>>
participant "Anycast LB" as lb <<External>>
participant "Edge Node" as edge <<External>>
participant "SRv6 Core" as core <<External>>
participant "BlueField DPU" as dpu
participant "Instance" as instance

client -> lb: HTTPS request via anycast IP
lb -> edge: Forward after WAF / rate limiting

edge -> core: SRv6 encapsulation\n(segment list from PCE)
core -> dpu: Route via optimal path\n(SRv6 decap at worker)

dpu -> instance: Deliver via OVS offloaded flow\nor direct to VF
note right of dpu: Steady-state traffic uses\nhardware-offloaded path.\nNo software in the loop.

instance --> dpu: Response
dpu --> core: SRv6 encap (reverse path)
core --> edge: Route back
edge --> lb: Forward
lb --> client: HTTPS response

@enduml
